OL,3,CMan who stabbed sister in neck and set
OL,4,Con fire to be sentenced in January
OL,6,FYou may find some of the details in
OL,7,Fthis article distressing.
OL,9,FA 27-year-old man who murdered his
OL,10,Fsister in her Portadown home and then
OL,11,Fset a fire outside his niece's bedroom
OL,12,Fis to be sentenced next month.
OL,14,FKornelijus Bracas, from Tresna Park in
OL,15,FRandalstown, stabbed his sister in the
OL,16,Fneck before setting her on fire while
OL,17,Fshe was still alive at the property on
OL,18,FChurch Street.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
