OL,3,CMan who stabbed sister in neck and set
OL,4,Con fire to be sentenced in January
OL,6,FHis 37-year old sister Alesia Nazarova
OL,7,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene
OL,8,Fwhilst her 12-year old daughter was
OL,9,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,11,FThe details emerged during a plea
OL,12,Fhearing at Belfast Crown Court where
OL,13,FCrown barrister Neil Connor KC said
OL,14,Fthe emergency services were called to
OL,15,Fthe property in the early hours of
OL,16,FMarch 21, 2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
