OL,3,CMan who stabbed sister in neck and set
OL,4,Con fire to be sentenced in January
OL,6,FBracas set five seats of fire in the
OL,7,Fhouse and when firefighters arrived,
OL,8,FMs Nazarova was found downstairs
OL,9,Fwhilst her daughter was rescued from a
OL,10,Ffirst floor bedroom.
OL,12,FParamedics also attended and whilst Ms
OL,13,FNazarova was pronounced dead a short
OL,14,Ftime later, Mr Connor said a
OL,15,Fsubsequent post mortem revealed she
OL,16,Fwas still alive when her brother set
OL,17,Fher on fire.
