OL,6,FShe sustained 60% burns and had also
OL,7,Fbeen stabbed between 14 and 15 times
OL,8,Fin the neck. She also sustained four
OL,9,Fstab wounds to her abdomen.
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said one of the wounds
OL,12,Fto her neck was "substantial" and
OL,13,Fwould have required urgent medical
OL,14,Fattention to prevent a loss of life.
OL,16,FBoth originally from Lithuania, Bracas
OL,17,Fhad been staying with his sister as
OL,18,Fwell as his niece prior to the murder
OL,19,Fafter he fell out with both parents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
