OL,6,FHe was arrested later that day on a
OL,7,Ftow path close to the Tesco car park
OL,8,Fin Portadown.
OL,10,FAt this point, he made no reply and
OL,11,Fpolice noted a strong smell of heating
OL,12,Foil on his clothing.
OL,14,FHe was found to be in possession of
OL,15,Fhis sister's bank card after being
OL,16,Fsearched, which he had used earlier to
OL,17,Fbuy items in Tesco.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
