OL,6,FDuring the course of two interviews
OL,7,Fconducted at Musgrave Street police
OL,8,Fstation, Bracas admitted killing his
OL,9,Fsister.
OL,11,FBracas also admitted setting five
OL,12,Fseats of fire with the intention of
OL,13,Fburning down the property and stealing
OL,14,Fthe bank card.
OL,16,FWhen asked by police to explain his
OL,17,Factions, Bracas said that in the early
OL,18,Fhours of March 21 he was packing to
OL,19,Fleave his sister's.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
