OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1766082497
OL,3,CMan who stabbed sister in neck and set
OL,4,Con fire to be sentenced in January
OL,6,FHe said they had an argument and that
OL,7,Fafter his sister screamed at him he
OL,8,F"snapped".
OL,10,FBracas also said that after she
OL,11,Fstarted climbing the stairs he grabbed
OL,12,Fher, placed her in a headlock and
OL,13,Fapplied pressure on her throat until
OL,14,Fshe stopped breathing.
OL,16,FHe said he then took a knife from the
OL,17,Fkitchen which he used to slit her
OL,18,Fthroat and that after this, he placed
OL,19,Frubbish around her body which he set
OL,20,Falight and also soaked towels in
OL,21,Fheating oil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
