OL,6,FBracas also admitted setting a fire
OL,7,Foutside his niece's bedroom door.
OL,9,FIn addition, Bracas claimed his sister
OL,10,Fdidn't appreciate him, treated him
OL,11,F"like garbage" and that he was made to
OL,12,Fdo household chores like babysitting
OL,13,Fhis niece.
OL,15,FBracas was previously convicted for
OL,16,Fassaulting both his mother and father
OL,17,Fand strangling his mother's cat.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
