OL,6,FHe subsequently pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fmurdering Ms Nazarova and stealing her
OL,8,Fbank card on March 21, 2023, as well
OL,9,Fas arson endangering the life of his
OL,10,Fniece and arson being reckless as to
OL,11,Fwhether the life of others would be
OL,12,Fendangered.
OL,14,FCiting several aggravating factors
OL,15,Fsuch as Bracas setting fire to his
OL,16,Fsister prior to her death, Mr Connor
OL,17,Ftold Madam Justice McBride it was the
OL,18,FCrown's view that "a higher starting
OL,19,Fpoint of 20 years or more should
OL,20,Fapply" when it came to sentencing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
