OL,3,CMan who stabbed sister in neck and set
OL,4,Con fire to be sentenced in January
OL,6,FSaying the offences were committed in
OL,7,Fa domestic setting, Mr Connor also
OL,8,Fraised the issue of deportation and
OL,9,Fasked Madam Justice McBride to "give
OL,10,Fconsideration" to this issue.
OL,12,FThe court also heard a portion of a
OL,13,FVictim Impact Statement written by the
OL,14,Fpartner of Ms Nazarova who spoke of
OL,15,Fhow they planned to marry.
OL,17,FIn his statement, he said he thinks
OL,18,Fabout Ms Nazarova "every day" and how
OL,19,Fhe wishes she could see their daughter
OL,20,Fgrowing up.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
