OL,6,FDefence barrister Kieran Mallon
OL,7,Fpointed out that during police
OL,8,Finterviews, his client was "candid and
OL,9,Ffrank" with police and made full
OL,10,Fadmissions to killing his sister.
OL,12,FMr Mallon said Bracas also "set out
OL,13,Fthe nature of his relationship" with
OL,14,Fhis sister to police which the
OL,15,Fbarrister described as "being akin to
OL,16,Fa Cinderella Syndrome" with Bracas
OL,17,Fbelieving he was "being used" and that
OL,18,Fhe "just snapped."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
