OL,6,FAfter listening to submissions from
OL,7,Fboth the Crown and defence, Madam
OL,8,FJustice McBride described domestic
OL,9,Fviolence as a "blight on society" and
OL,10,Fsaid the number of murders committed
OL,11,Fin domestic settings have "sky-rocked
OL,12,Fin this jurisdiction."
OL,14,FSaying she wanted time to reflect on
OL,15,Fwhat she had heard, the senior judge
OL,16,Fsaid she would impose the tariff - the
OL,17,Famount of time Bracas has to serve in
OL,18,Fprison before he is considered
OL,19,Feligible for release - on January 16,
OL,20,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
